  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This 2-stage, open-label study will evaluate safety and pharmacokinetics of ASTX727, as well
      as determine the dose for the study's second stage. In the second stage the selected dose
      will be confirmed and evaluated for clinical activity, including response rate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Dose levels for the study's second stage will be based on safety and pharmacokinetics.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
